'''227股灾''' ({{lang-en|Chinese stock bubble of 2007}}) 是一场发生在2007年2月27日的全球性[[股市|股市]]大跌。这个导致了市场数千亿的市值消失。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,254905,00.html |title=Wall Street Slammed After China Stock Woes - World Market Analysis | Financial News | Market Data | Stock Market News |publisher=FOXNews.com |date=2011-12-06 |accessdate=2012-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016160452/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,254905,00.html |archive-date=2012-10-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 在市场传言中国政府将要加息以试图抑制[[通货膨胀|通货膨胀]]，[[上海证券交易所综合股价指数|上海证券交易所综合股价指数]]（简称上证指数）下跌将近9%，成为10年内最大跌幅。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.forbes.com/home/markets/2007/02/27/china-shanghai-update-markets-emerge-cx_jc_vk_0227markets15.html |title=Black Tuesday In China |publisher=Forbes.com |date=2007-02-27 |accessdate=2012-06-06 |archive-date=2008-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081028232626/http://www.forbes.com/home/markets/2007/02/27/china-shanghai-update-markets-emerge-cx_jc_vk_0227markets15.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

亚洲市场的波动传导至全球市场。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2007-02/27/content_5780066.htm |title=Xinhua - English<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-09-11 |archive-date=2016-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160517230426/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2007-02/27/content_5780066.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 中国的[[股灾|股灾]]使得几乎所有全球市场的投资者产生不安。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/6399941.stm |title=Business | Share sale knocks Chinese market |publisher=BBC News |date=2007-02-27 |accessdate=2012-06-06 |archive-date=2007-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070310032537/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/6399941.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在中国股市下跌之后，[[美国|美国]]的[[道琼斯工业平均指数|道琼斯工业平均指数]]从12632点跌至12216点，下跌416点，跌幅3.29%。市场担心经济增长前景。这个是自2001年911恐怖袭击以来单日跌幅最多的一天。[[标准普尔500指数|标准普尔500指数]]下跌3.45%。卖单的速度非常迅速，不得不使用了一台额外的分析计算机。这个导致了道琼斯工业指数瞬间下跌200点。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://money.cnn.com/2007/02/27/markets/dow_drop/index.htm?postversion=2007022717 |title=printque |publisher=cnn.com |date=2007-02-27 |accessdate=2012-11-01 |archive-date=2019-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191224044732/https://money.cnn.com/2007/02/27/markets/dow_drop/index.htm?postversion=2007022717 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

